<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.5">
<l>akiṟkuṟaṭuñ cantaṉamu mampoṉṉu maṇimuttum</l>
<l>mikakkoṇarntu tiraiyuntum viyaṉpoṉṉit tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>pakaṟkaranta cuṭarāḻip paṭaiyāṉiv vulakēḻum</l>
<l>pukakkaranta tiruvayiṟṟaṉ poṉṉaṭiyē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr where the wide Poṉṉi [River] casts up waves, bringing</l>
<l>Pieces of aquila and sandalwood, fine gold, and beautiful pearls in abundance,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at the golden feet of the one whose divine belly concealed</l>
<l rend="indent">these seven worlds when they entered [into him],</l>
<l>The one whose weapon is the flaming discus which concealed the daylight.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
